NYT-06-07-98 1504EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19980607.0044 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-07 16:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8087 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  AM-SPORTS-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      06-07 0153
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE>
(HLW) 
</HEADLINE>
 AM-SPORTS-NYT-BUDGET
<TEXT>
<P>
   Add N.Y. Times News Service budget for papers of Monday, June 8:
</P>
<P>
   SPORTS
</P>
<P>
   (Coded s)
</P>
<P>
   BKN-BERKOW-COLUMN (Undated) _ Sports column on Jordan and the
NBA finals. By Ira Berkow.
</P>
<P>
