red-hot hype for Jim Carrey's ``The Truman Show'' with a powerful
$31.6 million at 2,315 theaters nationwide during the Friday-Sunday
period, studio sources said Sunday. By Dave McNary. (Will move in
the ``n'' California and ``a'' national news files.)
