<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19980607.0148 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-07 22:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
